datastring.name: event_descp
datastring.dstemplatestring:
The Medical Information Center (MIC) became aware of the following event on 15-Jun-2021. The reporter was the HCP Office Staff who
contacted the MIC on 15-Jun-2021 to provide information regarding the event as follows:

On 19-Feb-2019 the reporter stated that the patient started on Eylea in her right eye.

On 9-Jun-2021 the reporter stated that the patient received an injection with Eylea in her right eye.

On 12-Jun-2021 the reporter stated that the patient called into the office and stated that her right eye had pain and decreased vision. She was
advised to come in to see the on-call MD.

Note: Furthermore, there is another AE (REGEMC-85646) associated with this case.

There is no further information regarding the event at the time of this report.

Version 2, Jpostolski

On 22-Oct-2021 Regeneron Medical Information received a new source document. This version 2 AE report was filed to capture the new source
document.

No further information was available at the time of this report.
